snippet.title: Crypts of Death 2019 (Android) - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Fight through the graveyards and haunted forests, crypts and tombs filled with unspeakable horrors! Spin the daily treasure wheel, visit the shop and take control of four different warriors and their powerful magic weapons.

Free Android Mobile Game. Get it from the Google Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gamerealmmadness.cryptsofdeath
Ad-Free version available on Itch.io:
https://grmdev.itch.io/crypts-of-death

Music made by Purtsi. Listen the Official Soundtrack for free:
https://soundcloud.com/grmgamedev/sets/crypts-of-death
Purtsi's Youtube channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDwNoC1afNbx3T3713tCsNg

Test out the newest versions of games. We provide the newest, fresh builds for our patrons, and invite all of our supporters to take part in game design and quality control. Join now for only ONE DOLLAR a month! https://www.patreon.com/grmgamedev 

Follow us on Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/gamerealmmadness/

Visit on our Official Website:
https://gamerealmmadness.com/
